annotations:
Cut step, trip crack
 Cut down, trim back
 Call the florist, hope to make something pretty of it
Even though the the flowers are ‘old and faded’, Abby knows beauty can still be found in that. She believes that positive change can turn the flowers into something ‘pretty’.

WELCOME TO GENIUS' MAY 2021 SINGLES RELEASE CALENDAR!!!



For May 2021 album releases, visit this page



This page highlights the notable singles released in all genres throughout May 2021. Each song title includes a hyperlink to the corresponding lyric page.

HOW CAN YOU HELP?


Adding songs



If there’s a notable song you think should be listed here, add it! Or add a comment at the bottom of the page if you’re not sure. No self-promotion, please.


Adding lyrics



If you notice that any of the songs on this list haven’t been transcribed, go to the corresponding page and add in lyrics!


Updating dates



If we have any dates wrong, etc, add a comment at the bottom of the page.

search_results.lyrics:
Wasting Away Lyrics[Verse 1]
In the morning before
The weight of the day struck
I almost wanted you here to stay
But I got a headache
And you get impatient
You’re running while I hit the breaks

[Chorus]
If these cigarettes burn my chest
Then maybe I’ll cut out the rest
Can’t add another fire to the flame
Keep me in your mind I swear
Well maybe someday I’ll get there
But for now I'm stuck wasting away
[Verse 2]
You made up your mind
While you dig into mine
And I’m scared you won’t likе what I think
Is my misdirection
Clouding your vision
I never mеant to lead you this way

[Chorus]
If these cigarettes burn my chest
Then maybe I’ll cut out the rest
Can’t add another fire to the flame
Keep me in your mind I swear
Well maybe someday I’ll get there
But for now I'm stuck wasting away

[Bridge]
Ooh, ooh
Ooh, ooh
Ooh, ooh

[Chorus]
If these cigarettes burn my chest

Keep me in your mind I swear

description.plain:
Welcome to Christian Genius' January 2022 Singles Release Calendar!



For January 2022 album releases, visit this page



This page highlights all singles released in every genre of Christian music throughout 2022. Singles are listed with a hyperlinked title. Any songs that are not transcribed will have an indicated ⏳ next to the title.

How can you help?


Adding songs: If there’s a song you think should be listed on a specific calendar, edit the lyrics or add a comment at the bottom of the page for someone else to add.
Adding lyrics: If you transcribed a song, hyperlink the title and remove the ⏳ next to the song
Updating dates: If we have any dates wrong, etc, move the song to the correct date or add a comment at the bottom of the page.
